div.h1: TLB Management: invlpg vs CR3 Reload

div.p: asm ; Update page table entry mov [pte_addr], eax
asm ; Get current CR3 mov eax, cr3
asm ; Reload CR3 (flushes TLB) mov cr3, eax
Single page remap Change protections Unmap one page Minimal overhead needed
Context switch (different PD) Many pages changed Full address space switch Global pages need flush
